    • resize

      protected void resize(VariableMatrix mat, int numRows, int numCols)
      If the variable is a local temporary variable it will be resized so that the operation can complete. If not temporary then it will not be reshaped
      Parameters:
      mat - Variable containing the matrix
      numRows - Desired number of rows
      numCols - Desired number of columns
